data.description: PRIDE OF OWNERSHIP WITH AMAZING OUTDOOR FEATURES AND BEAUTIFUL GARDENS!  Welcome to this magnificent 4 bedroom estate inside the gated community of Brentwood Lakes.  Located on one of the largest lots in the community with a a beautiful privacy fence, attached birdcage screen enclosure to give you a huge outdoor entertainment area.  Very private lot that backs up to open easement with no neighbors directly behind.  Thousand spent in additional mature landscaping and gardens.  Newer upgraded A/C system, private well for irrigation, granite counters, crown molding and upgraded trim, newer carpet upstairs, solid surface flooring downstairs with no carpeting, vaulted ceilings stainless steel appliances, all fixtures and fans from original builder have been replaced and upgraded.  MUST SEE!
